    subtopic: "Malingering and Antisocial Personality Disorder",
    stem: `A 25-year-old man who has a history of agitations, multiple crimes, drug abuse, and theft comes to you with complaints of feeling sad, losing interest, insomnia, fatigue, and loss of appetite. He says that he is not using any drugs now, but he has been recently charged with a minor assault. Which one of the following is the most likely explanation for his behaviour?`,
