    subtopic: "OCD treatment - Exposure and Response Prevention",
    stem: `A 28-year-old man with obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD) has come for consultation. He has already been started on clomipramine and asks if there are other non-pharmacological treatment options for him. In response to his question, which one of the following options would you consider for him as a treatment for OCD?`,
