    subtopic: "Borderline personality disorder - Abandonment fears",
    stem: `A 27-year-old woman is about to get discharged from the hospital where she was admitted two weeks ago due to a psychological breakdown. When you tell her about the discharge plan, she says: 'Doctor, you cannot discharge me. If you do, I will hurt myself, and you will be responsible for that. Doctor Barkley knows me very well'. Which one of the following best describes the underlying cause of her behaviour?`,
