    subtopic: "Lewy body dementia - Visual hallucinations",
    stem: `An 84-year-old man who lives alone is brought to the emergency department by his neighbours. He has recently developed forgetfulness and peculiar behaviour. At night, the neighbours hear him shouting and saying that somebody is trying to break into his house, but nobody is there when they come and check. This behaviour started two months ago and has worsened progressively. Which one of the following conditions is most likely to have caused this presentation?`,
