    stem: `A 16-year-old boy presents to your GP clinic complaining of a recent decrease in school performance. He broke up with his girlfriend three weeks ago. He has been suffering from a lack of energy and sleep disturbances and feels like crying almost all the time. Which of the following would be the most appropriate next step in management?`,
