    subtopic: "Grief and Bereavement",
    stem: `A 67-year-old woman comes to your GP clinic six weeks after her husband passed away due to prostate cancer. She is sad and tearful, complains that she cannot sleep at night, and is afraid of the dark. She mentions similar feelings 32 years ago after she had a stillbirth. Which one of the following will help with prompt relief of her symptoms?`,
